space, and such a wonderful family. Josephine is so big now!!

Secondly, I cannot thank you enough for your kind offer reg. Berlin. Right
now we're very much in the air, with big questions about my work, my
startup, the boys' school in NYC, the rate of infection, etc. etc. etc. all
TBD. That said, please be ready for me to reappear in your inbox with a
request for introductions - I'm quite keen to explore living in Berlin and
as I understand it the housing component is perhaps the most complicated
element.

