ahead for a quick zoom just to catch up. On a purely personal level one of
the biggest gifts of the pandemic is a reaffirmation of our intention to
stay well connected with true friends, and I'd be keen to hear from you
directly about how you got through these crazy last few months!

With gratitude,
Josh

